    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with technical rigor, including proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry using polyurethane bushings for enhanced lateral stability. The VANOS system has been overhauled and the valve clearances adjusted to factory specifications within the last 5,000 miles. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a driven machine, the mechanical synchronization and throttle mapping remain exceptionally crisp, offering the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal performance.",
